s there, and nothing else held my attention but a man putting his hand on my shoulder. It was Ali,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33429,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/11\/uthman-third-adhan-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":43674,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: Uthman institutes third call to prayer on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Sa\u2019ib ibn Yazid reported: The announcement of Friday prayer was first made when the Imam would sit upon the pulpit in the time of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, as well as Abu Bakr and Umar, may Allah be pleased with them. In the time of Uthman,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36177,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/16\/qiyam-al-layl-moderate-voice\/","url_meta":{"origin":43674,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tahajjud: Reciting in moderate voice in night prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came out at night and he saw Abu Bakr who was praying with a low voice, and he passed by Umar ibn al-Khattab who was praying with a raised voice. When they met together, the Prophet said, \u201cO Abu\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33739,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/20\/sahaba-criticized-united\/","url_meta":{"origin":43674,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ikhtilaf: Companions criticized leadership but remained united","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Yazid reported: Uthman, may Allah be pleased with him, prayed four cycles at Mina. Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud said, \u201cI prayed it as two cycles with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, as well as Abu Bakr and Umar.\u201d Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Qurrah added: Abdullah then prayed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/salat-al-eid-then-khutbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":43674,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eid: The Prophet prays Eid, then gives sermon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: I witnessed the prayer on the day of Eid al-Fitr with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, may Allah be pleased with them. They performed the prayer before the sermon, then would deliver the sermon. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text